Snap a photo of your baby on their back in a safe sleep area and post it with the hashtag #SafeSleepSnap during the month of October for #SIDSAwarenessMonth. #SafeToSleep  https://t.co/ygAtDy964p  https://t.co/hYi8OukgwG

name: Lake Cumberland District Health Department
tweet: Mental illnesses can affect persons of any age, race, religion, or income. Mental illnesses are not the result of personal weakness, lack of character, or poor upbringing.  Mental illnesses are treatable.  #lcdhd  https://t.co/Qkvl2aLmnd

name: Lake Cumberland District Health Department
tweet: Are you worried that someone you love is at risk?  Follow your instincts and reach out for help.  Call 1-800-273-TALK or text HELLO to 741741.  For more information visit  https://t.co/lACgktkSa8 #lcdhd #SuicidePrevention #SuicidePreventionAwarenessMonth  https://t.co/npIA4esEuO
